metadata.name: Guardian Of The  Moon
metadata.description:
"Guardian of the Moon" captures the essence of an otherworldly guardian entrusted with the eternal task of protecting the lunar realm. The artwork emanates a captivating aura, drawing you closer to its sublime energy. 
The Sundays.wtf project represents a gathering of passionate creators and collectors who celebrate the ever-evolving landscape of the NFT movement.  
Indulge your senses in the enchanting world of "Guardian of the Moon," a testament to the creative spirit and collaborative brilliance of Me and Lahansubur
